{
  "stem": "13469.8",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 1.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have a very small vocabulary, as you probably have noticed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't use very many difficult, long, strange words.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I perhaps have difficulty expressing my feelings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's possible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, people will read all sorts of things into the Holocaust, like this looking for souvenirs in Buckingham Palace, you see?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I will say we learnt it in the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it's not really true.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, maybe it is true, but I would have learnt at a university or some other places just as much.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's just a habit, especially Ritchie has always been a natural scavenger and I've learnt it from him kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there's lots of things that-- that I do and I don't know and I don't do and I could say it was all due to the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe it was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How can you tell?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, I'm-- I'm a bit of a loner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's not until I've known anybody for quite a long time because I've become friendly with them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I become very friendly with people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I find it difficult to make friends on a quick basis kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I could say my children are very different from me in that respect.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think they're much more outgoing and extrovert than I am, although when I come on braking regulations and I give my talks everybody says I'm a great extrovert, because I keep mixing and jokes and all that sort of thing into braking regulations.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I-- in my talks, I mix in jokes with the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a lot of people think that's bad and a lot of people thinks that's my reaction to the Holocaust, that I joke about it.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
